he complete correspondence between Alfred Nobel and Sofie Hess.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Jul 2018) 0aChemical engineerszSwedenvCorrespondence. 4aDISCOUNT-B.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishz978311060403008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUTP eBook-Package Pilot 2017z978311066594908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2019z978311065878108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Pilot 2016-2017z978311060680508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press ebook package 2017z978311063896740uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/9781487513924423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781487513924.jpg  aPDA5EBK  a978-3-11-060403-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060680-5  University of Toronto Press Pilot 2016-2017  a978-3-11-063896-7  University of Toronto Press ebook package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-065878-1  University of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2019  a978-3-11-066594-9  UTP eBook-Package Pilot 2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aPDA14ALL  aPDA1ALL